[Student "S"]
{When WEST opens 2\C EAST has enough strength (9 points) for a positive response. But, 
because her suit is \Ds, she must jump to 3\D.

WEST thinks slam and uses Blackwood to discover that EAST holds one Ace. 

That's all EAST needs to know to bid 6\D.}

